SUMMARY:Volunteer Interest Booth
DESCRIPTION:Learn more about volunteering at the market this Saturday! \n\n\n\nVisit our volunteer booth at PSU Farmers Market on Saturday\, March 21\, 2026\, 9 AM – 2 PM to: \n\n\n\n\nLearn more about our five markets.\n\n\n\nMeet our staff and current volunteers.\n\n\n\nFind out about our volunteer program.\n\n\n\nAsk any questions you may have.\n\n\n\n\nYour involvement can significantly impact the success of our markets\, and we truly appreciate any time and energy you can offer. \n\n\n\nWe look forward to meeting you!
